# CODEOWNERS — mirrors AGENTS.md §7 Team Ownership matrix.
#
# Syntax: <pattern> <owner1> [<owner2> ...]
# Later matches override earlier ones. Patterns relative to repo root.
# All owners listed are GitHub team placeholders (@team-*) the org can
# rename via Settings → Teams to map to real groups/individuals.
#
# Rules of thumb:
# - A PR touching only a single owner area: that owner self-merges after CI.
# - A PR touching multiple areas: every touched owner must approve.
# - A PR touching an Owner port (infra/llm, crosscutting/glossary,
#   crosscutting/anchor, crosscutting/verifier): every downstream consumer
#   from AGENTS.md §7.3 must approve.
# - PRs to AGENTS.md / feature-specs / Sprint-Backlog-*.md require
#   @team-architect approval and a §-numbered rationale.

# =============================================================================
# Default fallback — anything not matched below.
# =============================================================================
*                                       @team-platform @team-architect

